[[File:QueensVictory-Challenge64.jpg|thumb|right|''Queen's Victory'' in flight.]]
'''''Queen's Victory''''' was a modified [[Bulk freighter/Legends|bulk freighter]] owned by [[Hawker Bryce-Kelley|Hawker Bryce-Kelly]] and his copilot [[Rypka]]. They used it to race a group of [[Alliance to Restore the Republic/Legends|Rebel]] wannabe's flying in the ''[[Limping Lady]]'' to the [[Planet/Legends|planet]] [[Zoma V]].<ref name="Limping">{{ChallengeCite|64|Limping Lady (article)}}</ref> Sometime after this, they landed the ship on the planet [[Reginard]] when they were trying to flee from ''[[Imperial Customs Frigate 517]]''. When they arrived there, however, they were not pleased when they discovered that there was not a Stellar Class [[Spaceport/Legends|spaceport]], as indicated by the homing beacon.<ref name="Death">{{ChallengeCite|76|Death by Triflexia}}</ref>

